" Vimium configuration using Colemak
unmapAll

" Navigation
map e scrollDown
map u scrollUp
map n scrollLeft
map i scrollRight
map E scrollPageDown
map U scrollPageUp

" Using Find
map / enterFindMode
map k performFind
map K performBackwardsFind

" Navigating history
map N goBack
map I goForward


" Manipulating tabs
map y nextTab
map l previousTab
